  <brief_title>Endometrial Biopsy as Diagnostic Method for Endometriosis and Endometrioma</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Evaluation of Endometrial Biopsy in the Diagnosis of Endometriosis and Endometrioma: a Double Blind Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
