  <source>Selcuk University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Our aim was to evaluate the efficacy of examining endometrial biopsy specimens for nerve
      fibers as a diagnostic test for endometriosis and endometrioma in a double-blind comparison
      with diagnostic laparoscopy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
